	CDN buckets:

		- fp.scea.com.c.footprint.net
			- fp.scea.com
			- webassets[a-j]?.scea.com


	Problematic hosts in *scea.com:

		- (www.)? ᵐ
		- webassets ᵐ
		- webassets[a-j] ᵐ

